[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "（システム）",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あれから少しして――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 965274698
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "『ランターナ紀行』、読ませていただきました。\n――とっても感動しました！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "あたしも読んだわよ。ユリエの文章って、なんだか\n景色が目の前に浮かぶのよね。ほんと感心しちゃうわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "二人とも、ありがとう。\n素直に嬉しいわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "こんなに素敵な文章を書けるなんて、\nユリエ先生、尊敬します！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……ふふ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "失礼する",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "ユリエ、君の紀行文が評判になっている。\n続編を望む読者の声も多い",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "そこで提案だ。無数島群域の紀行文を書いてみないか？　\n君なら、あの島々の姿も鮮やかに書けるだろう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "無数島群域……確かに、\nあそこは知らないことばかりで、興味あるわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "君の筆で、私たちにとって未知の地を記録してほしい。\n王国のためにもなる。もちろん報酬は出す",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……姉さん、どうするの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "無数島群域……いったいどんな所かしら",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私は、これからも旅の中で書き続けていく）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私の本を待っている人がいるから）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "シャルロッテ",
		"romanized_name": "Shallotte",
		"model_path_hash": "322297020958821866",
		"text": "ユリエさんについていかなくてよかったの？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5588667421325366917",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……本が届けば、姉さんのことは分かるから。\nそれに――",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "姉さんは絶対に帰ってくる。\n私が保証する",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（楽しみに待っているわ。姉さん）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "レスナ・シュテルネンリヒト",
		"romanized_name": "Resna Sternenlicht",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "「果ての大陸」を目指す腕利きの錬金術士。\n無数島群域航海の合間、アトリエに帰ってきた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル・フォル＝エルスリート",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell Voll=ErsLied",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "凄腕の魔法使い。シャルロッテの師匠。\nレスナと共にアトリエを訪れた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]